The three arrivals got situated and began thier planning.

The old bot stood up adressing the other two. "I want the two of you to
start searching this planet for the dominant DNA we need, Foxfingers go out
and search this sorry excuse for a planet. keep me advised of your
progress." He turned his head toward the other bot, "My daughter, you will
begin setting up my lab, when Foxfingers returns we will need to begin
quickly." He turned back to the red and brown bot he'd adressed first. "And
Foxfingers, try to stay out of trouble this time."

With a quick glance and a sly smile the bot known as Foxfingers exited the
ship. "I'll return my lord, with everything you need." He lowered a
hoverboard to his feet and began his journey south. "I'll begin with the
larger concentration of Maximals and work my way back from there."

His journey to what will one day be Africa had begun, he hoped for an
uneventful voyage but kept his gaurd up just in case.
